{"word":"G4563 - σαρόω - saróō - sar-o'-o - Sweep","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σαρόω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">saróō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">sar-o'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Sweep</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பெருக்கு"},{"paragraph":"to sweep, clean by sweeping"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a derivative of <b>&#x03C3;&#x03B1;&#x03B9;&#x03C1;&#x03C9;</b> <b>sairo&#x0304;</b> (to <i>brush</i> off; akin to <a href=\"#/G4951 - σύρω - sýrō - soo'-ro/4951\">G4951</a>) meaning a <i>broom</i>; to <i>sweep:</i> - sweep.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}